column5: Hello all, Hows it goin? Just wondering where you would suggest to go for some walleyes and northerns in the first week of June next year? thanks for your input.

Here in Manitoba drive to lakes that carry alot of trophy walleye's and pike.Tramping lake,Reed lake,Athapapaskow,Faiford river and a few small lakes around my house which i won't mention those are my honey holes for my trophys.FISH ON.
